HEADWORD: Glyoxalic
<hw>Gly`ox*al"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or designating, an aldehyde acid, intermediate
between glycol and oxalic acid.</def> <altsp>[Written also
